motornet.nets#

Module contents#

This module contains four submodules, with each submodule implementing a series of subclasses based off typical tensorflow objects. In other words, this module can be conceptualized as an extension of tensorflow for the purpose of bridging motornet.plants classes and tensorflow itself.
